Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:18.74,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Even though it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.95,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…even though I feel sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:29.28,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…in the court I feel just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:37.48,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,When I hear the ball flying, my heart races.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:41.56,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Receive. Toss. Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:46.55,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,One-two, one-two! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:49.35,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,But sometimes I cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:52.41,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,I'm a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:01:00.68,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Through the tears and sweat, putting up a youthful fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:08.82,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…under the blue sky, I just want to scream:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:16.98,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:26.12,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.68,0:01:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 004\NBall torn to pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow…\N- Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{正確のスパイク}Such an accurate spike…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{丸で精密機会のようだわ}…almost like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right… she's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたは新しいキャプテンの、あいはらこずえさんね。}Are you the new captain,\NAyuhara Kozue-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどり、みどりじゃないの？}Midori! Midori, is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{なか？}Naka? Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{ みどり、どうしたて言うの？}Midori, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日転校して来たの。}I've transferred today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{パパの会社この富士見市にも、\N????ことになったのよ。}My dad's company opened a new office here in Fujimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{そ。懐かしいわ。ね、何年ぶりかしら？}- Ah. Long time no see.\N- How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川みどりさんってね、小学校であたしたちと同じクラスだったのよ。}Hayakawa Midori-san and I were in the same class in the grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{五年生の時だったかな。}We were in the fifth class, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{確か母さんの方へ転校してたなけど、また戻って来たのね。}If I remember, she moved to her mom's place, but she returned now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san's family is in top management, so they're very rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもかっこよなくなバレー部に入ってると思わなかったわ。}Who would've think you'd enter a cool volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは始めてばかりなの、まだだめよ。}I've just started, so I'm not any good yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{それにみどり、凄いじゃないの。今見てたわよ。}But you're something else, Midori. I could see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんな凄い一人バレー見たら始めてよ。}Really. It's my first time seeing someone this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{京都へ行ってから、ずっとバレーやってたの。}I've been playing ever since I went to Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あの???ならあいはらさんだってできるわね。}But this much should be easy for Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、やってみなければ…}Well, I'd have to try…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{できないはずないわよ。だって、こずえさんはキャプテンでしょ？}There's no way you couldn't do it. After all, Kozue-san, you're the captain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日からバレー部に出っていただくわ,キャプテンさん。}From now on, I'll be coming to the volleyball club, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、練習よ。大会はもう直ぐなのよ。}Well, let's practice. The tournament's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{ＯＫ}OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃね。}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしも明日から練習させてもらうわ。}I'll be coming to practice too from tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、よろしく。}I hope we get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい！キャプテン！}Hey, captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部の新キャプテン!}The volleyball club's new captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さん！}Tsutomu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{あいはらくん、どうかしたのかい？なんだが、???にしているだけど。}Ayuhara-kun, did something happen? You seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん、別に。}No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{練習で疲れたのかい？}Tired from the practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{とうがいちく選手権大会のスケジュールは決まったんだろ。}The tournament's schedule was decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{新キャプテンあいはらこずえいながら、それでは困るじゃないか。}It'd be troublesome if the new captain Ayuhara Kozue wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{大会優勝目指して,絶対に頑張った貰わなくちゃ。}You have to do your best to win the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、努さん。なんだい？}- Hey, Tsutomu-san.\N- Hm? What it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さん！}Tsutomu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さあん！}Tsutomu-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさんだ！}- It's Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの…商会しよう。}Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら。あいはらさん。}Oh. Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんだ。君たちもうしってたのか。}What, you know yourselves already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。あたしは今日バレー部に入ったの。キャプテンあいはらさんには、も挨拶にしたわ。}Yes. I entered the volleyball club today. I've already greeted captain Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうだったのか。}That's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さん、あいはらさんと同じクラスでもないのに、中良い見たいのね。}Tsutomu-san, you're not in the same class as Ayuhara-san, but I feel you get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。実は、僕達親戚なんだ。}Yeah. To tell you the truth, we're related.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕のおばさん、つまり僕の母さんの妹の結婚した相手が、あいはらくんのお父さんの弟。}My aunt, in other words my mom's younger sister, is married to Ayuhara-kun's father's younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{つまり、叔父さんなんだ。分かる？}In short, her uncle. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと??しいけど、間違いない親戚なんだ。}It's a little roundabout, but we're most definitely relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:05:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、そうなの？ね、あいはらさん。あたしと努さんは、幼児?からずっと一緒だったの。}Oh, that was it? Ayuhara-san, I've known Tsutomu-san ever since kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{小学校で?????の、仲良し成ったのよ。}We became good friends at elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさんが京都に行くまえに、家が僕の家の近所だったんだよ。}Midori-san was my neighbor before she went to Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、努さん。努さんの所へパパから???ちょうど良かったわ。一緒に行きましょう。}Hey, Tsutomu-san. I was about to deliver a welcome gift to your family from my papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょうど良かったわ。一緒に行きましょう。}It's good that I met you here. Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、さようなら。}We'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{さようなら。}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川みどりさんは転校してきた。}Hayakawa Midori-san has transferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部に何が起こりそう気がする。}I feel that something's about to happen in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部に何が起こりそう気がする。}I hope I am thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimi Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Teachers room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{どもありがとうございました。}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:06:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{いあ。お父さんからわざわざ電話をいただく間でもなく、わたしも運動部に力を入れるべきだとは考えていたんだよ。}No, no. After having received the call from your father, I thought I should put an effort into the sport clubs as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{まそれには先ずバレー部を強くすることだね。}Well, volleyball club comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{劣等生だと言われていたのグループの生徒達も少しずつ成績が割ってきてますわ。}The students who were said to be poor performing are slowly improving their grades too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{これもスポーツお始めたおかげでしょうね。}I guess this is thanks to the sports, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{そ。 それだけでも、スポーツと言うものが以下に大切ものか。 はっきりしている。}Indeed. This alone is enough to consider sports important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{学校はあくまで学力第一です。しかしま、クラブ勝つどに、力を入れていくもいいでしょう。}The school is mostly about academic achievements. But yes, putting effort into club victories should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝でもしてくれれば、高名はげろことなりますからな。}If they do win, it might increase the school's prestige.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do my best. We will certainly win the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{バイバイ、さようなら}- Bye bye!\N- See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら？皆どうしたのかしら。}Hm? I wonder where's everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{親分！じゃなくて、キャプテン！}Chief! I mean, captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたの？皆、練習の時間だって言うのに。}What's the matter? It's practice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日からね、体育館で練習できるになったよね。}We can practice in the gym since today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？体育館で？}Huh? In the gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちのバレーの試合お見て、教頭先生や皆がはっと気づいたのよ。}After our match, the teachers and everyone have finally noticed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{これは運動部に力を入れるべきである。得に、バレー部にってさ！}They want to support sport clubs more. Especially the volleyball club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほんと？そよ。気がつく？おそいくらいよ。}- Really?\N- Yep. They're slow if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{といっても、本当はみどりが教頭先生に頼みこんだからなんだ。}But in reality, Midori has asked the head teacher for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Hayakawa-san did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{？ち持ってきて。うん。}- Leave them here.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川さん、ありがとう。ここで練習できるなんて本当に素敵。}Thank you, Hayakawa-san. It's wonderful that we can practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{寒い天気外で練習する辛いもん。}We no longer need to worry about cold weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{はー早川さんで凄い力があるのね。}Ha- Hayakawa-san sure is powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはお金持ちだからよ。お金持ちには?}It's only natural when she's so rich. With wealth comes great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうか。でも早川さんはバレー部に入ってくるよかったわね。}Right. It's good that Hayakawa-san has joined us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここで練習できるし、それに早川さんのスパイクは凄いわね。}Not only we're able to practice here - her spike is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川さん、どもありがとう。}Thank you, Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？なんのこと？}Hm? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここ練習できること?}Ah, for being able to practice here? It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:08:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all for the victory in the tournament. Now, let's practice. You better do you best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{不要グループで有名だったそうじゃないの。 聞いたわよ。}I heard about your reputation of the "useless group".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？それは言わないでよ。耳が痛いわ。}- Huh?\N- Don't say that, it makes my ears hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an old story. We're different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! We're serious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because of the volleyball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Ever since we started playing-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for Ayuhara-san, you'd get expelled from the school, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way over the line. Who said it? I won't forgive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that from Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, it's okay to be open about this. Didn't I make myself clear about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We truly owe Ayuhara-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,…but expulsion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's cruel.\N- Yes, it's just heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't get ahead of yourself!\N- Easy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let it be. You're here now, right? If we win the tournament, let's just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Stick it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice time. Toss the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's… that's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ayuhara-san.\N- Katsuragi-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're such a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori was like that since elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's wealthy, alone and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fujimi Academy hasn't won a match even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a team that is a capable of winning the upcoming tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I also think that we need a resolute captain. Don't you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course.\N- Hayakawa-san would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. After all it's thanks to her that we can practice in a gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If Midori was the captain, we'd get far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You have some never saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think gathered us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, Ayuhara-san did badmouth us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think our captain would do that? That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori, what are you scheming? Stop being so egocentric. If you only think about yourself, you'll trip soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, it's about time you said something!\N- Kashiwagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But she…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign my role as a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be the captain, but didn't ask the head teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am thinking of the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Also it's not up to oneself to become or quit being a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a decision of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's skip the practice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself. You're the only one who can be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Our chief must be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than who is or isn't the captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,…I am afraid if Hayakawa-san will torn apart our club that we've just managed to form.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball is about team work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose to that selfish lass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When captain has it together, everything works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up my love for volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a strong and elegant team as much as Hayakawa-san. No, I want it even more than her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hold it while I pull the other side.\N- Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Hayakawa-san, you don't need to do such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't do. No matter how good I am, I am still a new member. It's only natural that I perform newcomers' tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san is so splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san never did such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because she's the captain. I am different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd do this even if I was the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,After all when one loves volleyball, they're fine doing any important task.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Way better than Ayuhara-san ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, way better!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are. I came all the way from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kashiwagi-san is really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,People like Midori-san are restless since their childhoods until they're treated like a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But why does she want to become a captain so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be fine if I wasn't captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that. It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I could probably talk her out of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,…but it'd be better if you resolved it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With the tournament around the corner, it's the most important time for your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, new captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you found your purpose in the volleyball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did you become like a balloon without air again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit the volleyball!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, with the way you're now…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have the patience for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen if we had a fight now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball club will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I love volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why even if Hayakawa-san did become a captain, I'd still be okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? There's no stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was delivered directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san. I want to talk with you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please meet me at 7 AM at the volleball's club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Hayakawa-san is up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we here so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to lock the door yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized only this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be bad if our equipment was stolen, and this is why I've asked you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was it. I don't think anyone would steal anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be all right, but let's go and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball club's room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It it's unlocked all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You come at the right moment. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Whoa.\N- How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The net is torn too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who hates volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This? It was lying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably used this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ayuhara-san, you're pretty dreadful person.\N- What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ayuhara-san, you're holding a grudge against me, is that right?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, are you saying it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anyone but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way any of us could destroy important equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished listening to our captain. Aren't you, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The title of captain doesn't fit Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed in you. I didn't think you're such a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, do you want to become the captain this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, just say so openly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't resort to writing roundabout letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to pick a fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I think it's clear that you don't deserve the title of captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am trying to do my best for the club, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,…what should I do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow!\N- Brand new!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,These were all funded by Hayakawa-san's father. It sure is nice to be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With these we'll be able to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone decided that I'll be our new captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori, if you don't knock it off, I'm not going to tolerate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, don't you think that's too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's the decision of our members.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It already has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, won't you be coming to practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'd be bothersome to everyone if you don't listen to me from tomorrow on. I want to make a strong team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, looks like you lost to Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Defeat doesn't suit you, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll endure it if it means improvement for the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Bu…\N- How far can you go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouze-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kozue-chan.\N- Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, auntie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've returned earlier today and you seem off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you feel unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good then. I got a call from Hayakawa-san's house today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to invite you to a dinner, Kozue-chan. They'll even send a car for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This way please. Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.\N- Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Midori's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, where is Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be here in a second. Sit, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, it was me who called you here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori became your captain. I hope you get along well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uhm…\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want to ask you is…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,…is for you to do your best under Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show Midori to the world by putting her in the Fujimi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that Midori's true power goes unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If your volleyball club became Japan's best, Midori's fame would obviously rise too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As a bonus, I'll buy each of you whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:22:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball isn't a place to make yourself popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're asking you to work hard so that Midori alone gets famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori-san, I'll make myself clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.82,0:22:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With your way of thinking, there's no way you'll get to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go back.\N- Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I say to offend her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. I have to think of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She has some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.63,0:22:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she think volleyball is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped that if I persevered, everything will work out, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:23:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, I'm sorry. I have to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me who cut balls and the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.46,0:23:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'll be hard for us to get famous under Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I did it. It's very embarrassing and I regret it now. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to make up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of our club… for teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you forgive me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best on our way to the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah… thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I need Ayuhara Kozue-san's power for the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.26,0:23:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to playing, I'm the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll certainly become a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.93,0:23:56.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After Midori and Kozue called a truce, the coach Hongou…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:23:59.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,…immediately begins a hard training.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:04.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But the peace doesn't hold long and soon enough, a problem with staff members arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.28,0:24:08.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even so, the coach continues with his training.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.68,0:24:15.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Under his guidance, Kouze and Midori's true rilvarly becomes ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:19.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.
